<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
    <title>E-mail de notification</title>
    <style media="all" type="text/css">
    /* -------------------------------------
    GLOBAL RESETS
------------------------------------- */
    body {
      font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.3;
      -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
      -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
    }
/* -------------------------------------
    BODY & CONTAINER
------------------------------------- */
    body {
      background-color: #f4f5f6;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .body {
      background-color: #f4f5f6;
      width: 100%;
    }
/* -------------------------------------
    TYPOGRAPHY
------------------------------------- */
    p {
      font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: normal;
      margin: 0;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    a {
      color: #0867ec;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    .link-button {
      background-color: #EEDF7A;
      border-radius: 5px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #000000;
      font-weight: bold;
      min-width: 300px;
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 5px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
/* -------------------------------------
    RESPONSIVE AND MOBILE FRIENDLY STYLES
------------------------------------- */

    @media only screen and (max-width: 640px) {
      .main p,
      .main td,
      .main span {
        font-size: 16px !important;
      }
      .wrapper {
        padding: 8px !important;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 0 !important;
      }
      .container {
        padding: 0 !important;
        padding-top: 8px !important;
        width: 100% !important;
      }
      .main {
        border-left-width: 0 !important;
        border-radius: 0 !important;
        border-right-width: 0 !important;
      }
    }
    /* -------------------------------------
    PRESERVE THESE STYLES IN THE HEAD
------------------------------------- */

    @media all {
      .ExternalClass {
        width: 100%;
      }
      .ExternalClass,
      .ExternalClass p,
      .ExternalClass span,
      .ExternalClass font,
      .ExternalClass td,
      .ExternalClass div {
        line-height: 100%;
      }
      .apple-link a {
        color: inherit !important;
        font-family: inherit !important;
        font-size: inherit !important;
        font-weight: inherit !important;
        line-height: inherit !important;
        text-decoration: none !important;
      }
      #MessageViewBody a {
        color: inherit;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: inherit;
        font-family: inherit;
        font-weight: inherit;
        line-height: inherit;
      }
    }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
  <div class="wrapper" style="text-align: center;">
    <div class="header" style="background-color: #343131; margin-bottom: 2 rem; text-align: center;">
      <img class="email-masthead_logo" src=https://www.tres-joueurs.me/assets/logo-9bec149a3f9a84b4ed41ee81e996f5112c055de5fb2e821d20f3627db05ede1f.png width="200px" height="120px">
    </div>
    <div class="content" style="margin: auto; background-color: #FFFFFF; text-align: center; max-width:600px; padding: 10px;">

      <p>Bonjour <%= @resource.username %>!</p>

      <p>Tu as demandé à réinitialiser ton mot de passe. Tu peux y parvenir en cliquant sur le lien ci-dessous.</p>

      <p><%= link_to 'Nouveau mot de passe', edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token) %></p>

      <p>Si tu n'es pas à l'origine de cette demande, ignore cet email.</p>
      <p>Ton mot de passe ne sera pas modifié tant que tu n'auras pas finalisé la procédure via le lien.</p>

    <p>A bientôt sur très.joueurs !</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p style="color: #9a9ea6; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1px;"><small>Tres Joueurs © - 2024</small></p>
      <a href="https://www.tres-joueurs.me" style="color: #9a9ea6; text-align: center;"><small>tres-joueurs.me</small></a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
